  "detailed_description": "After a long run you finally found a ride, too bad it has no brakes.<br><br>                                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297370/extras/894a68db662a76505aaf1671058683db.webp?t=1622294854\" width=79 height=27 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Drive through countless waves of zombies and hit as many of them as you can<br></li><li>You have no fuel or time limits<br></li><li>Collect cash to buy car upgrades and weapons</li></ul><br>                                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297370/extras/9415d99f3e82e5c98913915b839b63d1.webp?t=1622294854\" width=79 height=27 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Randomly generated arena each time you play<br></li><li>Auto aiming weapons to help you reach top scores<br></li><li>Car upgrades<br></li><li>Achievements and global leaderboards</li></ul><br><br>                                                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297370/extras/26c3c8dd1fdf29d574d93c8765b00ecd.avif?t=1622294854\" width=150 height=150 /></span><br><br>ZDD is a sequel to ZDR released back in 2013 on mobile platforms and the prequel to whatever zombie game we make next",
